{"tid":1785007,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國旅行團去年加國車禍 死傷者家屬索賠近30億港元","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:28:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"528fa5dd267559db778d58b9983d0249af050169","tid":1785007,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"一個中國旅行團去年在加拿大遇到車禍，造成3人死亡，超過20人受傷，死傷者家屬入稟當地法院，要求賠償5億加幣，相當於近30億港元。<br />\n<br />\n根據相關法庭文件，被控的美籍華裔司機在意外發生時，除了超速駕駛，更用手機發短訊，之後旅遊巴失事，撞到路邊岩石翻側。死傷者的家屬向這名司機、旅遊巴公司及交通部門提出索償，指司機未能做好駕駛工作，旅遊巴公司亦未能正確培訓司機、未確實檢查車輛。涉事司機早前已經被起訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%98%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E6%AD%BB%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E8%BF%9130%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83-051830303.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2585%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E8%25BF%259130%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583-051830303.html&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7lc%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=ad2554ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%98%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E6%AD%BB%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E8%BF%9130%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83-051830303.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e82555991df3919840563bc8e68deed5e47d874","tid":1785007,"uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">美籍華裔司機</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先佢係中國人，中國人整死中國人有30億賠？發緊夢？"},{"pid":"03be5b59d19e7b1a6f19ee3faa160baaaddbc83a","tid":1785007,"uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0